comment:
* State (oom score) for processes known to activity manager.
 * {@hide}

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_EMPTY
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means not hosting any components (cached).

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_SYSTEM
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's a system process.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_PERSISTENT
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's a persistent process.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_BACKUP
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's hosting a backup/restore agent.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_INSTRUMENTATION
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's hosting an instrumentation.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_ACTIVITY
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's hosting an activity.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_BROADCAST_RECEIVER
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's hosting a broadcast receiver.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_PROVIDER
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's hosting a content provider.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_STARTED_SERVICE
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's hosting a started service.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_FOREGROUND_SERVICE
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's hosting a foreground service.

variables.name: HOSTING_COMPONENT_TYPE_BOUND_SERVICE
variables.comment:
* The type of the component this process is hosting;
     * this means it's being bound via a service binding.

variables.name: mHostingComponentTypes
variables.comment:
* The types of the components this process is hosting at the moment this snapshot is taken.
     *
     * Its value is the combination of {@link HostingComponentType}.

variables.name: mHistoricalHostingComponentTypes
variables.comment:
* The historical types of the components this process is or was hosting since it's born.
     *
     * Its value is the combination of {@link HostingComponentType}.
